    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 997.1 Carrera S is a superlative example of Stuttgart engineering, maintained to a concours standard. The 3.8L flat-six delivers linear power delivery across the rev range, featuring a robust M97 power plant with the uprated factory IMS bearing. Its 6-speed manual transaxle offers short, precise throws, paired with a factory-spec limited-slip differential for optimal corner-exit traction. The chassis remains taut, benefiting from Porsche Active Suspension Management (PASM) and zero bushing deflection. Meticulously serviced with a documented history, the underbody is as clean as the Arctic Silver metallic finish. This is a turn-key, investment-grade driver for the discerning purist.",
