      "description": "This vehicle is a true time capsule, preserved in showroom condition since day one. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish with zero rock chips or imperfections, having been professionally ceramic coated and strictly garage-kept. Inside, the cabin remains immaculate; the premium leather seats show no signs of bolster wear, and the interior still carries that new-car scent. Every electronic feature, from the high-fidelity sound system to the climate control, functions flawlessly. Under the hood, the engine bay is spotless, reflecting a rigorous maintenance schedule performed exclusively by certified technicians. This car comes with a complete paper trail of service records, all original keys, and the owner\u2019s manual. It drives exactly as it did the day it rolled off the lot\u2014tight, responsive, and powerful. For the discerning buyer who accepts nothing less than perfection, this is a rare opportunity.",
